Idk if there has been one of these..if not:

This is a game where you continue 1 word from the last persons post to form a sentence.You can do -----------  to start a new sentence but you can't randomly stop one when it hasn't finished.
Example:
Player 1: One
Player 2: Day 
Player 3: I
Player 4: Went 
Player 108: to
Player 4: KFC
Player 6: ------------             
             Yesterday,

You can make sentences as long as you want.
I'll start :One
